  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing public awareness, influencing legislation and improving the training of lawyers in support of promoting the use of jury trials in Kazakhstan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to increase take up of the right to jury trial in Kazakhstan through producing a series of videos aimed at raising awareness of this right among the general population and policy-makers, producing a manual for lawyers on the conduct of jury trials, and training 15-20 practising lawyers at each of three training sessions in different major cities. This is an opportunity to use UK experience and expertise in jury trials to strengthen governance and rule of law in Kazakhstan.</narrative>
  </description>
